included.title: User Experience Researcher

included.summary:
I am a user experience researcher with over 6 years of testing and improving products. 

By providing companies with unbiased deep-dives into their customers' experiences, user research helps product teams navigate uncharted waters before launch. In contrast, testing an already existing product validates previous product decisions or helps to highlight areas of improvement. I believe the best user researcher comes from an interdisciplinary background, as having an unbiased perspective is key in implementing any methodology successfully. 

Any research is only as effective as the communicator âÂ I strive to deliver my insights accurately to product managers and designers alike. I produce reports tailored to the recipient depending on the next steps in the development cycle. In addition, I find collaborative workshops invaluable due to the team input and ability to lean on past learnings. In all, my global function in an organization is to usher a product team towards success by involving a user's perspective throughout the process.
included.headline: User Experience Researcher
